ZH: 传染病是由病原微生物引起的疾病。
EN: Infectious diseases are caused by pathogenic microorganisms.

ZH: 流感是一种常见的传染病。
EN: Influenza is a common infectious disease.

ZH: 传染病可以通过空气传播。
EN: Infectious diseases can spread through the air.

ZH: 传染病严重影响了公共卫生。
EN: Infectious diseases seriously affect public health.

ZH: 传染病可以通过接触传播。
EN: Infectious diseases can spread through contact.

ZH: 预防措施可以帮助避免传染病的传播。
EN: Preventive measures can help prevent the spread of infectious diseases.

ZH: 小心卫生是预防传染病的关键。
EN: Good hygiene is key to preventing infectious diseases.

ZH: 疫苗可以预防一些传染病。
EN: Vaccines can prevent some infectious diseases.

ZH: 医生在控制传染病方面发挥着重要作用。
EN: Doctors play a crucial role in controlling infectious diseases.

ZH: 传染病爆发时，政府通常会实施隔离措施。
EN: When infectious diseases break out, governments often implement quarantine measures.

ZH: 传染病的传播速度很快。
EN: Infectious diseases spread quickly.

ZH: 病原体穿过眼结膜可能导致传染病的传播。
EN: Pathogens passing through the conjunctiva of the eye may lead to the spread of infectious diseases.

ZH: 传染病在集体场所传播更容易。
EN: Infectious diseases are more easily spread in crowded places.

ZH: 传染病对弱势群体的影响通常更为严重。
EN: Infectious diseases often have a more severe impact on vulnerable populations.

ZH: 在传染病流行期间，人们应该避免大型公共聚会。
EN: During an outbreak of infectious diseases, people should avoid large public gatherings.

ZH: 一旦发现传染病病例，立即通报卫生部门。
EN: Report cases of infectious diseases to the health department as soon as they are discovered.

ZH: 有些传染病可以通过食物传播。
EN: Some infectious diseases can be spread through food.

ZH: 必须采取紧急措施来防止传染病爆发。
EN: Emergency measures must be taken to prevent an outbreak of infectious diseases.

ZH: 传染病的症状可能会在潜伏期出现。
EN: Symptoms of infectious diseases may appear during the incubation period.

ZH: 传染病爆发会对社会稳定造成影响。
EN: Outbreaks of infectious diseases can have an impact on social stability.
